## Development environment

This repository is scaffolded from
[project-template](https://github.com/P4suta/project-template). Tooling
is pinned declaratively in `mise.toml` (the single source of truth for
tool versions); recipes are exposed through the `Justfile`.

```sh
just bootstrap    # mise install + lefthook install — run once after clone
just lint         # all configured lint passes
just test         # whatever the active language layers expose
just ci           # the full pipeline CI runs, fail-fast
```

`just hooks` installs the lefthook pre-commit / commit-msg / pre-push
hooks; anything that would fail in CI fails locally first. Commit
messages follow [Conventional Commits](https://www.conventionalcommits.org/),
enforced by `committed` via the commit-msg hook.

